text: Diana Carolina Ospina Pineda (born 3 March 1989) is a Colombian international footballer who plays for local club Envigado as a midfielder. She represented Colombia at the 2011 FIFA Women's World Cup in Germany and 2015 FIFA Women's World Cup in Canada as well as the 2016 Summer Olympics in Brazil. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Colombian women's footballers Category:Colombia women's international footballers Category:2011 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:2015 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Olympic footballers of Colombia Category:Footballers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games competitors for Colombia Category:Footballers at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Colombia Category:Pan American Games medalists in football Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games
